PP-OCRv6_medium_det_onnx — redistribution
=========================================

This repository mirrors the ONNX export of PaddleOCR's PP-OCRv6 medium
text-line detection model.

Upstream source:
  https://huggingface.co/PaddlePaddle/PP-OCRv6_medium_det_onnx
Original author: PaddlePaddle / PaddleOCR team
License: Apache License 2.0 (see LICENSE)
Reference: arXiv:2606.13108

The model weights (inference.onnx, ~59 MB) are committed as a plain
(non-LFS) git blob AND attached as a GitHub Release asset. raw.githubusercontent.com
serves the committed blob directly (portable across restrictive egress
allowlists); the release asset is an alternative where that host is reachable.
See scripts/fetch_model.sh or the README for retrieval.

No modifications have been made to the model. The text config files
(inference.json, inference.yml) are copied verbatim from upstream.
